{"tid":102285,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"做gym飲食問題","createTime":"2017-01-31T13:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T14:52:07.000Z","uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08e38764c66f9ec63d0f813e93fc50b2b6cc5217","tid":102285,"uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T13:43:33.000Z","msg":"平時會係夜晚做gym 大概8,9點到<br />\n做完gym唔知食咩好<br />\n依家177cm 80kg<br />\n有啲gym底 但體脂比大概21到 肥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想減體脂同時又增肌食咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n份量又點計?<br />\n<br />\ngoogle過但好多都唔啱自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152c4ffdef2b567bc5e08feb2490c5b79b4439f3","tid":102285,"uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T13:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ed17af2cd57bc57534f39966ec9125ec3af3de","tid":102285,"uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T13:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4f2d62f19fdf5c95a67886844becacfba3eff7","tid":102285,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:02:50.000Z","msg":"消脂無得同增肌一齊做"},{"pid":"073d1cac6b7fbd58f159c9b4df6c76f80743fbd0","tid":102285,"uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:12:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>消脂無得同增肌一齊做</blockquote><br />\n求解"},{"pid":"068bd7a3e31f3e62cd585fc8ed001332f34479b5","tid":102285,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:13:36.000Z","msg":"想問操完PC肌食咩補番好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c3cef916fbf9fab29da732411d7c5c337e1e86","tid":102285,"uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77703115499c8c25270928198365501a6cf6a13","tid":102285,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>消脂無得同增肌一齊做</blockquote><br />\n求解</blockquote><br />\n消脂係calories deficit <br />\n增肌係calories surplus <br />\n如果消脂增肌可以一齊做<br />\n健美先生洗乜off season 果陣上磅再cut down?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之脂肪同肌肉就一齊增加或減少 你控制到既只有其中一樣增快d同減快d<br />\n唔好再諗不切實際既野"},{"pid":"d60bc1a7042ad3c976dfd07f65cba400f73585b9","tid":102285,"uid":64320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>消脂無得同增肌一齊做</blockquote><br />\n求解</blockquote><br />\n因為增肌要食大量碳水化合物（carbs)   因為有助肌肉增長。 而carbs 本身都含有糖分同脂肪。<br />\n而消脂以蛋白質為主 ，carbs就盡量有咁少就得咁少 ，以阻止多餘糖分同脂肪。咁就容易達致消脂效果<br />\n如果當你消脂既時候再食咁多carbs 就只會進行唔到消脂過程 <br />\n所以有分 bulking &amp; cutting."}]}